{"TopicId":188455,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Target Problem","CreatedByName":"Dr. Omicron","CreatedById":196927,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-24T01:45:36Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Omicron","CreatedById":196927,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-24T01:45:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://prntscr.com/pa2uvu\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://prntscr.com/pa2uvu\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have already smashed my f4 key but it still wont show the box in non map screen\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-24T02:40:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved to Gameplay Questions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-24T03:19:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe target indicator doesn\u0027t show until you get to 100kms or less from the target. Is that what you\u0027re asking about?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Omicron","CreatedById":196927,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-24T03:41:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223676583\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188455\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221569295182\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 minutes ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe target indicator doesn\u0027t show until you get to 100kms or less from the target. Is that what you\u0027re asking about?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was like 97m from my Space station and it still did not show.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fulgur","CreatedById":195204,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-24T06:54:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe [F4] key shows boxes around the control point of your target \u003Cstrong\u003Eonly\u003C/strong\u003E at distances larger than 150m. Back off a little bit, and the purple box will appear. Double-click it to set it as your target and it will go green. Then it will show up as close as you go.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}